data.title: Strenthening 18-19 Parali To Gangakhed Estimate
data.meta_description:
Strenthening 18-19 Parali to Gangakhed Estimate - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides information on a proposed road project, including:

1. The project involves the partial strengthening of the Kharwandi-Rajuri- Beed- Parali-Gangakhed-Loha NH361F road section from Parali to Gangakhed (KM 157/0 to 162/000). 

2. The road connects several districts and talukas in the region and its improvement is considered important. 

3. The section from Parali to Gangakhed is proposed for partial strengthening based on instructions from the Superintending Engineer of the National Highway Circle in Aurangabad.
